{
  "stem": "8002.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- actually, it's in his own house, the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rabbi was Itche.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Itche Berkowitz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was very strict.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were but six students, actual small kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We started to go to cheder when we were six years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he used to say, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you didn't do the way he wanted to do, you had to put out your hand on the table.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he used to take a twig.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he'd [? strike ?] over the fingers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you said ouch, then he hits you more, until you didn't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then you had to take the finger and point and say it over and over and over again until you did it correct.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he used to keep us there for quite a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If we wanted to go out, play, and do something else, but he says, you're in the cheder now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you're going to stay until you learn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But when I was nine years old, I already knew all the five [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we already learned [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That is unusual, because [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], you learn when you're about 11.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE], he taught us very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were good students.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we learned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that's why all my Christian friends says, you're too smart for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I can't play with you, because you're way ahead in school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I says, I'm not smart, I just wanted to learn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And after school was finished, we had do our studies and do our homework.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we sit down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And before we went, we had to go out to play, we had to do all our homework that my father and mother sure that we do our homework.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
